## Customization

Workflow presets are defined in `workflows/presets/`:
- `full-sdlc.yaml`
- `rapid-dev.yaml`
- `maintenance.yaml`
- `quality.yaml`
- `quick-fix.yaml`
- `feature-implementation.yaml`
- `simple-fix-issues.yaml`
- `simple-improve-quality.yaml`
- `simple-new-feature.yaml`

You can modify these files or create your own presets.
